    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels at MRL 2. The remaining 6 factors are appropriately designated not-assessed consistent with MRL 2 scope. Uncertainty quantification via comprehensive Monte Carlo sampling across all stochastic inputs has been completed and 95th-percentile hemolysis index bounds remain below the RH < 1 acceptance criterion. The overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision for the Class II CPB device.",
